that the hotel industry

00:56:40.010 --> 00:56:41.450
and the taxicab industry,

00:56:41.450 --> 00:56:44.640
there're gonna be interests
pushing back the other way.

00:56:44.640 --> 00:56:45.880
And they're gonna be pointing to things

00:56:45.880 --> 00:56:48.812
like the fact that I
think many Uber drivers,

00:56:48.812 --> 00:56:50.758
I don't really know what I'm
talking about here, right?

00:56:50.758 --> 00:56:51.591
(Harry laughs)

00:56:51.591 --> 00:56:52.900
So I'm gonna say to be irresponsible.

00:56:52.900 --> 00:56:56.290
